## Set up

1. Install uv https://docs.astral.sh/uv/getting-started/installation/ if you don't have one.
2. `uv sync` to install dependencies

## Running experiments

- To run experiment with our method:
`uv run experiments/train.py --simulator_name lv --method_name dro_ub --n 1024 --epsilon 1.0` 
where `lv` stands for Lotka Voterra simulator.

- To run experiment with our method + epsilon selection.
`uv run experiments/train_and_optimise.py --simulator_name lv --n 1024 --metric kl_cal --optimiser BO`

